# You will need a RapidAPI key to access the weather data:

# 1. Go to https://rapidapi.com/
# 2. Sign up for a free account
# 3. Subscribe to the "Weather API" service (there's a free tier)
# 4. Copy your API key into a .env file that you would create in the root of this project, replacing the placeholder text below:

RAPIDAPI_KEY=your_actual_rapidapi_key_here